  "name": "Viper Swarm",
  "pfs": {
    "availability": "Standard",
    "subtype": "pfs",
    "type": "stat_block_section"
  },
  "schema_version": 1.4,
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Viper Swarm",
      "sections": [
        {
          "image": {
            "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png",
            "name": "Additional Lore",
            "type": "image"
          },
          "name": "Slithering Packs",
          "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
          "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
          "sources": [
            {
              "link": {
                "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
                "aonid": 276,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Monster Core 2",
              "page": 294,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "subtype": "sidebar",
          "text": "Despite their solitary natures, snakes come together in swarms for purposes of hibernation or mating. However, a few species have learned to stick together and coordinate their hunting efforts, leading to slithering packs of predatory snakes.",
          "type": "section"
        }
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
            "aonid": 276,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core 2",
          "page": 294,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "The frightening mass of shining scales, gleaming eyes, and fangs dripping with venom that constitute a viper swarm has brought an end to many an unlucky adventurer. Normally nocturnal, these notoriously aggressive snakes strike at anything that comes within reach, be it limb or weapon. Their venom is a potent toxin that leaves victims shaky and weak. Those who are lucky may receive a warning strike without venom before being attacked in earnest.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
    {
      "link": {
        "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
        "aonid": 276,
        "game-obj": "Sources",
        "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
        "type": "link"
      },
      "name": "Monster Core 2",
      "page": 294,
      "type": "source"
    }
  ],
